{"tid":586043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵去年盈利升64% 達168億 另月底宣佈票價調整","createTime":"2018-03-09T07:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T14:40:45.000Z","uid":188,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd7e7434ea36b3887ff0f97cf7e1f5f3d0dd86f","tid":586043,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"港鐵公布2017年度業績報告，去年盈利上升64%至168億元。另外，客量打破歷年紀錄，全年乘客量達20億人次。 港鐵表示，今年向乘客提供的回贈會按利潤及服務表現作出安排，並至少提供6個月的每程3%回贈。 至於港鐵的票價調整，會於今個月底政府公布運輸業工資指數變動後，才有公布。"},{"pid":"cbc81256ebc4fd5c9c025a8e90c8467a6475ef20","tid":586043,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999712d8326005362e23d709a6a018d39f297f51","tid":586043,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:59:10.000Z","msg":"係咁倚比個九五折回程優惠跟住加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e456644190d51976c143b28687496718785aea8e","tid":586043,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"999712d8326005362e23d709a6a018d39f297f51","tid":586043,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:59:10.000Z","msg":"係咁倚比個九五折回程優惠跟住加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"5%都冇 得3% 多撚謝"},{"pid":"f3ea42ed460b2a2d851a18a845b6fa8668d975be","tid":586043,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e5a4aeec34d7424824ce610c6502301d36c98c","tid":586043,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e456644190d51976c143b28687496718785aea8e","tid":586043,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"999712d8326005362e23d709a6a018d39f297f51","tid":586043,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"